[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;35m\u001b[1mв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;35m\u001b[1m  Demo 4: Quality Gates & Self-Improving Agents\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;35m\u001b[1mв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җв•җ\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;90mThis demo shows Pattern 3: Quality gates that make agents self-improving.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;90mStarting from Link Shelf + search (Demo 2), we add favorites with:\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[0;33mACT 1: PLAN APPROVAL\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Teammate submits plan вҶ’ Lead reviews вҶ’ \u001b[0;31mREJECT\u001b[0m (missing migration)\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Teammate revises вҶ’ Lead reviews вҶ’ \u001b[0;32mAPPROVE\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[0;32mACT 2: HOOKS ON TASK COMPLETION\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    TaskCompleted hook fires automatically:\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    в”ңв”Җв”Җ npm test ................... must \u001b[0;32mPASS\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    в””в”Җв”Җ grep console.log ........... must be \u001b[0;32mCLEAN\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Hook \u001b[0;31mFAILS\u001b[0m вҶ’ agent fixes вҶ’ hook re-runs вҶ’ \u001b[0;32mPASS\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[0;35mACT 3: COMPOUND LEARNING\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "    Lead updates AGENTS.md with new learnings\r\n    Next session reads these вҶ’ avoids same mistakes\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[0;32mв–ё\u001b[0m \u001b[1mUsing Demo 2 output (Link Shelf + search) as base...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.142, "o", "\u001b[0;32mв–ё\u001b[0m \u001b[1mCopying base app from demo-2...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.123, "o", "  \u001b[0;32mвҶ’\u001b[0m Copied base app files\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[0;32mв–ё\u001b[0m \u001b[1mInstalling dependencies...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[4.183, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.016, "o", "\u001b[0;32mв–ё\u001b[0m \u001b[1mLaunching Claude Code with Agent Teams + quality gates...\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "  \u001b[0;90mCLAUDE_CODE_EXPERIMENTAL_AGENT_TEAMS=1\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
